http.title: St. John Lutheran Church-HOME
http.html:
Everyone is always welcomed here!

Come & Worship with us every Sunday at

10:00 AM - Worship with Holy Communion


     









We look forward to see you this week and Easter!


PLEASE Check out our EVENTS & NEWS pages for special and exciting things that are happening         at St. John!


Come as you are... Not as you should be

You Are Always Welcomed at St. John...
       �to rest in the presence of God and let God's peace rest richly in your heart!  


You are welcome to be one with others who follow God in an often God-less world; to pray, learn, connect, and grow with a different kind of family.  You are welcome to be faithful; to live with purpose and without apology the life God call you uniquely to live.  

We know that life is hectic, fractured, and driven by so many different loyalties.  At St. John we fix our eyes on the Author and Perfecter of faith; the God of the Bible who through His Son Jesus Christ renews our souls and by His Holy Spirit reinvigorates our living! 


You are always welcomed to come to St. John anytime!
 
We look forward to 
seeing you soon!




Our Pastor is Rev. Mark D. Hanchett

St. John Lutheran Church
550 E. Wilbeth Road
Akron, Ohio 44301
Phone: 330-773-4128

E-mail: stjohnlcms550@sbcglobal.net

Like us on Face Book

Akron, OH

Parallels is a worldwide leader in virtualization and automation software that optimizes computing for consumers, businesses, and Cloud services providers across all major hardware, operating systems, and virtualization platforms.

For the Cloud, Parallels automation and virtualization software enables cloud services providers to rapidly and profitably deliver the widest range of cloud services that small businesses want and need.
